Hallucination
    FACTUAL_ERROR
    REASONING_FAILURE

-----------------------------------------
-----------------------------------------

Perfomance Metrics
    Accuracy = proportion of questions answered correctly
    Error rate = 1 - accuracy
    Hallucination counts = among incorrect answers, how many were labeled:
    FACTUAL_ERROR
    REASONING_FAILURE


